r />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S8cpe0x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS8cpe0x.jpg&h=940a0d14&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"塊扒算好差，把木刀係鋸唔開塊肉。本身塊肉就好硬身，但廚師手法我相信冇問題。<br />\n<br />\n雞翼好ok，水牛城好得，濕辣醬係面個雞皮都係脆。<br />\n<br />\n另外一款雞翼就配搭藍芝士醬。Woo，好食，個雞翼普通。主要係個藍芝士醬好味，好溫和唔知溝左咩，個腳臭香味變左清香咁，但咸度比起直接食淡好多。"},{"pid":"900346fd52106f8b1d9299fa80a36eff6c1d9828","tid":2462510,"uid":330582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:52:28.000Z","msg":"有錢人lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}